  title: "The game doesn\u2019t restart properly when I press 'Play' again \u2014
    it resumes from level 2. Why?"
  text: This happens because `levelNumber` and `scoreTotal` are `static` variables,
    meaning they persist across scenes. You need to manually reset them using `GameManager.ResetStaticData()`
    when starting a new game.
